race.comment: BRIEF SPIRIT (1) has been knocking on the door of a maiden victory of late and gets plenty of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Looks the one they will all have to run down in this staying contest. FLIRTING WITH FIRE (6) just ran into one better at Toowoomba at the latest effort and is drawn to get a gun run in transit from the inside marble. Top-three conveyance on that sort of form. NIENNA (9) will be rock-hard fit for this and hoop Tomizawa sticks following that last-start placing. In the mix for some minor money. CONTINENT (5) gets the services of Moor in the irons and draws ideally in gate two. One for the exotics.
